      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 9,
      "message": "I have done it this way for consistency of approach across the policy docker images.\nThe script will be invoked by Jenkins job, for example, for policy engine see: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=ci-management.git;a=blob;f=jjb/policy/policy-engine.yaml;h=c364ef537f7de467d2559112e8288b79f368bcae;hb=ebb12b047923822d34ca712d6307b0ff06a43324\nThe referenced \"include-raw-docker-*.sh\" scripts invoked docker_build.sh and docker_merge.sh",
